# ============================================================================
# TEAM VAULT USAGE NOTES
# ============================================================================
#
# After renaming this file to `.gitignore`:
#
# 1. Clean existing .obsidian/ state:
#    ```powershell
#    Remove-Item .obsidian/cache -Recurse -Force
#    Remove-Item .obsidian/workspace*.json -Force
#    ```
#
# 2. Verify selective tracking:
#    ```powershell
#    git status
#    # Should show: plugins.json, templates/, snippets/
#    # Should NOT show: workspace.json, cache/, plugins/*/data.json
#    ```
#
# 3. Stage shared configs:
#    ```powershell
#    git add .obsidian/plugins.json
#    git add .obsidian/community-plugins.json
#    git add .obsidian/templates/
#    git commit -m "feat: add team vault configuration"
#    ```
#
# 4. Document team-required plugins in README.md
#
# 5. Test on clean clone to verify plugin installation
#
# ============================================================================
